<reference id="class_packet">
    <title><ph keyref="Packet"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc" props="cpp">用于配置 <xref keyref="Packet"/> 实例。</ph></shortdesc>
    <refbody>
        <section id="prototype">
            <p outputclass="codeblock">
                <codeblock props="cpp" outputclass="language-cpp">struct Packet {
  const unsigned char* buffer;
  unsigned int size;
};</codeblock>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters" deliveryTarget="details" props="cpp">
            <title>属性</title>
            <parml>
                <plentry props="cpp">
                    <pt>buffer</pt>
                    <pd>发送或接收数据的缓冲区地址。
                        <note>声网建议将 <codeph>buffer</codeph> 设置为大于 2048 字节的值。否则，可能会遇到未定义行为（如崩溃）。</note>
                    </pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry props="cpp">
                    <pt>size</pt>
                    <pd>发送或接收数据的缓冲区大小。</pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml>
        </section>
    </refbody>
